  <text xml:lang="ta">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink224-kilavi">  iṟceṟippuṇarnta talaimakaḷ āṟṟāḷāyt talaimakaṉ ciṟaippuṟattāṉākat tōḻikkuc colliyatu. </p>
        <p xml:lang="en">What the heroine, who realised that she [would be] confined to the house, said to the confidante while the hero stood behind the hedge.</p>
      </div>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink224">
<l>amma vāḻi tōḻi nammalai</l>
<l>maṇiniṟaṅ koṇṭa māmalai veṟpiṟ</l>
<l>ṟuṇinī raruvi nammō ṭāṭa</l>
<l>leḷiya maṉṉā lavarkkiṉi</l>
<l>yariya vākutaṉ maruṇṭaṉeṉ yāṉē</l>
</lg>
<lg xml:lang="en">
  <l>  O friend! </l>
  <l rend="indent">[the times] he bathed with us in the waterfalls of clear waters, </l>
  <l rend="indent2">along the slopes of the dark mountain that had taken on a sapphire hue,  </l>
  <l rend="indent3">were once so effortless. </l>
  <l> I worry that [such times would] now be rare for him.</l>
  
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
